Uncover library for Android

Packages 
Package Description
com.ames.uncover
This main package contains the central model class you are expected to use.
com.ames.uncover.impl
These classes may be cool to read about but please do not use them in your implementation directly, or at least avoid.
com.ames.uncover.primary
This package defines classes you need to use for implementing the data provider that fetches data for you model (in chunks, using the background thread).
